    <item>
      <title>英国赤字超标，债务占 GDP 的 100% 对里夫斯造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/uk-deficit-overshoots-in-blow-to-reeves-as-debt-hits-100-of-gdp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府在本财年的前五个月的借款额高于预期，这使得财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯面临下个月提高税收以实现预算平衡的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/uk-deficit-overshoots-in-blow-to-reeves-as-debt-hits-100-of-gdp</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 06:11:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场上涨，印尼卢比有望创下 1 月以来最佳单周表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/idr-usd-indonesian-rupiah-set-for-best-week-since-january-as-bonds-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着资本流入增加，印尼债券价格上涨，印尼盾本周有望创下 1 月份以来的最佳表现。印尼央行表示，将允许印尼盾升值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/idr-usd-indonesian-rupiah-set-for-best-week-since-january-as-bonds-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 05:18:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最后一刻指数被剔除，全球波动性最大的大型股票应声下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/indonesia-s-barito-renewables-tumbles-after-ftse-index-removal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富时罗素 (FTSE Russell) 表示将在预计加入日期的第二天将这家印尼电力巨头从其指数中删除，随后 PT Barito Renewables Energy 股价跌至每日涨停。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/indonesia-s-barito-renewables-tumbles-after-ftse-index-removal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 03:26:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
